    "description": "IIFL Finance is actively seeking a talented and motivated Senior Financial Analyst to join our dynamic team in Vadodara. This is an excellent opportunity for professionals who are passionate about making a real impact in a fast-growing organization.\n\nAbout IIFL Finance:\nIIFL Finance is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Implement and maintain internal controls and audit procedures\n• Liaise with banks, regulators, and financial institutions\n• Prepare and analyze financial statements, reports, and budgets\n• Monitor financial performance against targets and provide variance analysis\n• Develop financial models and projections for business planning\n• Manage accounts payable and accounts receivable functions\n• Prepare annual reports and investor presentations\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Post Graduate Diploma in relevant field\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Bloomberg Terminal\n• Proficiency in Budgeting\n• Proficiency in Income Tax\n• Proficiency in QuickBooks\n• Proficiency in Ind AS\n• Proficiency in SAP FICO\n• Proficiency in Python for Finance\n• Proficiency in Credit Analysis\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Flexible working hours\n• Referral bonus program\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Vadodara, Gujarat, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with IIFL Finance!",
